## Safety Protocols

- **Data Protection**: Encrypt all financial data locally
- **Privacy First**: Never transmit personal financial data externally
- **Backup Required**: Save all budget changes before modifications
- **Validation**: Cross-check all calculations and recommendations
- **Rollback Ready**: Generate undo scripts for all budget changes

